title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When using the JarExporter function, the exported jar file includes itself, causing the application to go out of sync.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to prevent the application from going out of sync.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Use the JarExporter function to export a jar file. 
2. Verify that the exported jar file does not include itself.
